    "Name": "Griffin",
    "Details": "The Capellans have rebuilt the Griffin from the skeleton up to take advantage of their new stealth armor. The engineers selected a XL fusion engine to allow for the larger LRM-15 launcher and Guardian ECM system; thirteen double-strength heat sinks are required to keep the design reasonably cool. Further upgrades include an Artemis IV targeting system to improve the accuracy of the missile rack and an ER PPC. Concerns about the fragility of using an XL engine was settled by allotting an additional 1.5 tons of armor. Finally, CASE protection for the ammunition bins was vital; while incapable of protecting the bulky engine, it allows the pilot to eject safely in the event of an ammunition explosion.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Battle Fists</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.05</color></b>",
